             produced the piece, valued at three pounds.)</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178705230020"></xptr>Court. Is your warehouse a part of the dwelling-house? - Yes, the dwelling-house is over it.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>Coming home from Whitechapel, I saw a man drop this on the ground, and I picked it up, and I was going to give it to the man, and they caught hold of me.</p>
               <p>
